[DQC.US.0011.6829] It is expected that StockholdersEquity with a value of 1,755,200,000 reported in the network role http://www.wfscorp.com/role/ConsolidatedBalanceSheets should be equal to the dimensionally qualified concept, StockholdersEquityIncludingPortionAttributableToNoncontrollingInterest with the dimension us-gaap:StatementEquityComponentsAxis = us-gaap:ParentMember and a reported value of 1,755,100,000 multiplied by 1. This value appears in the network role http://www.wfscorp.com/role/ConsolidatedStatementsOfShareholdersEquity. This error occurs when the dimensionally qualified fact is not equal to the value input for the non dimensional item.
The properties of this us-gaap:StockholdersEquity fact are:
Period : 2018-03-31 Dimensions : Unit : USD Decimals of StockholdersEquity : -5 Decimals of StockholdersEquityIncludingPortionAttributableToNoncontrollingInterest : -5 Rule version: 9.0.0RC1 - http://www.sec.gov/Archives/edgar/data/789460/000162828018005281/a2018q110qdoc.htm 2632
